              5 out of 5 stars
              A Visual and Audio Treat! Sony Delivers Big on Quality.
              From picture clarity to sound output, Sony has truly nailed it with this model. 🔹 Picture Quality (10/10) The 4K Ultra HD panel with X-Reality PRO and Dolby Vision brings out deep blacks, punchy colors, and a realistic contrast. Watching nature documentaries, action movies, and even IPL matches is a visual treat. The HDR support works beautifully, especially in darker scenes. 🔹 Sound Quality (8.5/10) The inbuilt 20W speakers with Dolby Audio are surprisingly good for casual viewing.
